                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper's Washington Correspondent reports on Johnson's veto of the
                    Supplementary Bill, calling it "the ablest of Mr. Johnson's efforts."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
